          Choose if you want us to use this image for quality improvements.
        </div></div> <div class="col-md-6"><button class="btn btn-outline-primary" data-action="click-&gt;improvedialog#reject" style="margin-top: 15px;">
          No, don't contribute
        </button> <div style="font-size: 75%; opacity: 0.75;">
          Choose if you do NOT want us to use this image for quality improvements.
        </div></div></div></div> <div class="col-md-12 text-center"><div data-target="improvedialog.accepted" style="display: none;"><p class="lead">Your image will be used for future improvements of remove.bg.</p> <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="document.getElementsByClassName(&quot;mfp-close&quot;)[0].click()">Close</button></div> <div data-target="improvedialog.rejected" style="display: none;"><p class="lead">Your image will NOT be used for future improvements of remove.bg.</p> <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="document.getElementsByClassName(&quot;mfp-close&quot;)[0].click()">Close</button></div></div></div> <div class="vue-component" data-vue-file="./cookies.vue" data-vue-props="{&quot;renderAs&quot;:&quot;banner&quot;,&quot;hotjarEnabled&quot;:true,&quot;country&quot;:&quot;PK&quot;,&quot;explicitConsent&quot;:false,&quot;showRejectAll&quot;:true,&quot;ip&quot;:&quot;2001:4860:7:1422::ff&quot;,&quot;consentShareSites&quot;:[],&quot;cookiePolicyVersion&quot;:&quot;2025-08-04&quot;,&quot;t&quot;:&quot;{\&quot;consent\&quot;:\&quot;By using remove.bg you agree to the use of cookies. You can find details on how we use cookies in our \\u003ca target=\\\&quot;_blank\\\&quot; href=\\\&quot;/cookies\\\&quot;\\u003eCookie Policy\\u003c/a\\u003e.\&quot;,\&quot;eu_consent\&quot;:\&quot;We use cookies to improve your experience and for analysis. You can deactivate them anytime.\&quot;,\&quot;header\&quot;:\&quot;Cookies\&quot;,\&quot;open_settings\&quot;:\&quot;Information \\u0026 Settings\&quot;,\&quot;modal_header\&quot;:\&quot;Cookie Settings\&quot;,\&quot;modal_cookie_info\&quot;:\&quot;To provide you a great experience and for certain functions, we use so-called cookies. Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device. For more info and a full list of cookies we use go to our \\u003ca target=\\\&quot;_blank\\\&quot; href=\\\&quot;/cookies\\\&quot;\\u003eCookie Policy\\u003c/a\\u003e.\&quot;,\&quot;always_on\&quot;:\&quot;Always on\&quot;,\&quot;close\&quot;:\&quot;Close\&quot;,\&quot;essential\&quot;:{\&quot;header\&quot;:\&quot;Essential Cookies\&quot;,\&quot;description\&quot;:\&quot;are necessary for features which are essential to use our site, such as signing up, logging in or making purchases.\&quot;},\&quot;functional\&quot;:{\&quot;header\&quot;:\&quot;Functional Cookies\&quot;,\&quot;description\&quot;:\&quot;are used to enhance the functionality of this site, e.g. by remembering your settings and preferences to provide you with a better experience.\&quot;},\&quot;performance\&quot;:{\&quot;header\&quot;:\&quot;Performance Cookies\&quot;,\&quot;description\&quot;:\&quot;help us to measure traffic and usage data and to analyze how our Services are used in order to provide you with a better user experience and maintain, operate and improve our Services. These cookies may be set by us or third-party providers whose services we have added to our websites and apps.\&quot;},\&quot;targeting\&quot;:{\&quot;header\&quot;:\&quot;Targeting cookies\&quot;,\&quot;description\&quot;:\&quot;help us show you ads that are useful to you on our websites or on third-party websites, and measure the effectiveness of the relevant ad campaigns.\&quot;},\&quot;accept_selected\&quot;:\&quot;Accept selected\&quot;,\&quot;accept_all\&quot;:\&quot;Accept all\&quot;,\&quot;reject_all\&quot;:\&quot;Reject all\&quot;,\&quot;manage_cookies\&quot;:\&quot;Manage Cookies\&quot;}&quot;}" data-vue-on="{}" data-v-app=""><div data-v-ef75e0c9=""><div data-v-ef75e0c9=""><!----></div><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" id="consentModal" class="modal" data-keyboard="false" data-backdrop="static"><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-md-centered"><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="modal-content"><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="modal-header border-0 pb-0 px-1"><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="container"><h5 data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="modal-title">Cookie Settings</h5></div></div><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="cookie-consent-info py-2 py-md-3 px-1"><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="container"><p data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="mb-0">To provide you a great experience and for certain functions, we use so-called cookies. Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device. For more info and a full list of cookies we use go to our <a target="_blank" href="https://www.remove.bg/cookies">Cookie Policy</a>.</p></div></div><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="modal-body px-1"><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="container"><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="row consent-class"><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="col-9 col-md-10 pr-0"><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="d-flex align-items-center"><span data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="consent-class-header d-block">Essential Cookies</span><span data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="always-on ml-2 text-uppercase font-weight-bold d-block">Always on</span></div><p data-v-ef75e0c9="">are necessary for features which are essential to use our site, such as signing up, logging in or making purchases.</p></div><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="col-3 col-md-2 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"><label data-v-25adc6c0="" data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="vue-js-switch toggled disabled"><input data-v-25adc6c0="" type="checkbox" disabled="" class="v-switch-input"> <div data-v-25adc6c0="" class="v-switch-core" style="width: 55px; height: 25px; background-color: rgb(0, 128, 9); border-radius: 13px;"><div data-v-25adc6c0="" class="v-switch-button" style="width: 19px; height: 19px; transition: transform 300ms; transform: translate3d(33px, 3px, 0px);"></div></div> <span data-v-25adc6c0="" class="v-switch-label v-left" style="line-height: 25px;">ON</span></label></div></div><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="row consent-class"><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="col-9 col-md-10 pr-0"><span data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="consent-class-header block">Functional Cookies</span><p data-v-ef75e0c9="">are used to enhance the functionality of this site, e.g. by remembering your settings and preferences to provide you with a better experience.</p></div><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="col-3 col-md-2 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"><label data-v-25adc6c0="" data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="vue-js-switch toggled"><input data-v-25adc6c0="" type="checkbox" class="v-switch-input"> <div data-v-25adc6c0="" class="v-switch-core" style="width: 55px; height: 25px; background-color: rgb(0, 128, 9); border-radius: 13px;"><div data-v-25adc6c0="" class="v-switch-button" style="width: 19px; height: 19px; transition: transform 300ms; transform: translate3d(33px, 3px, 0px);"></div></div> <span data-v-25adc6c0="" class="v-switch-label v-left" style="line-height: 25px;">ON</span></label></div></div><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="row consent-class"><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="col-9 col-md-10 pr-0"><span data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="consent-class-header block">Performance Cookies</span><p data-v-ef75e0c9="">help us to measure traffic and usage data and to analyze how our Services are used in order to provide you with a better user experience and maintain, operate and improve our Services. These cookies may be set by us or third-party providers whose services we have added to our websites and apps.</p></div><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="col-3 col-md-2 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"><label data-v-25adc6c0="" data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="vue-js-switch toggled"><input data-v-25adc6c0="" type="checkbox" class="v-switch-input"> <div data-v-25adc6c0="" class="v-switch-core" style="width: 55px; height: 25px; background-color: rgb(0, 128, 9); border-radius: 13px;"><div data-v-25adc6c0="" class="v-switch-button" style="width: 19px; height: 19px; transition: transform 300ms; transform: translate3d(33px, 3px, 0px);"></div></div> <span data-v-25adc6c0="" class="v-switch-label v-left" style="line-height: 25px;">ON</span></label></div></div><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="row consent-class"><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="col-9 col-md-10 pr-0"><span data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="consent-class-header block">Targeting cookies</span><p data-v-ef75e0c9="">help us show you ads that are useful to you on our websites or on third-party websites, and measure the effectiveness of the relevant ad campaigns.</p></div><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="col-3 col-md-2 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"><label data-v-25adc6c0="" data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="vue-js-switch toggled"><input data-v-25adc6c0="" type="checkbox" class="v-switch-input"> <div data-v-25adc6c0="" class="v-switch-core" style="width: 55px; height: 25px; background-color: rgb(0, 128, 9); border-radius: 13px;"><div data-v-25adc6c0="" class="v-switch-button" style="width: 19px; height: 19px; transition: transform 300ms; transform: translate3d(33px, 3px, 0px);"></div></div> <span data-v-25adc6c0="" class="v-switch-label v-left" style="line-height: 25px;">ON</span></label></div></div></div></div><div data-v-ef75e0c9="" class="modal-footer justify-content-center w-full flex-wrap flex-md-nowrap"><button data-v-ef75e0c9="" type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-block mt-0 mr-0 mr-md-1 mb-2 mb-md-0 ml-0" data-dismiss="modal">Accept selected</button><button data-v-ef75e0c9="" type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-block mt-0 mr-0 mr-md-1 mb-2 mb-md-0 ml-0" data-dismiss="modal">Reject all</button><button data-v-ef75e0c9="" type="button" class="btn btn-banner-success btn-block mt-0 ml-0 mb-0" data-dismiss="modal">Accept all</button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>





